reviewText: This is a great effective video.  My friend and I are huffing and puffing in just 6 minutes.  Love the warm up and cool down.  Don't skip it.

It's a workout that gets your heart pumping, but can be done easily and it is over before you know it! She makes it easy to follow and doesn't go too fast. It'll whip your tail at first, but provides great results! Highly recommend this DVD!
